, Michael Manahan, Michael Manotoc, Alfonso Martinez.<ref name=\"Royalties\"/>\n\nMartinez, along with [[Carl Guevarra]] joined the cast of [[Star Magic Presents]]:  [[Abt Ur Luv]] which was revamped to [[Abt Ur Luv|Abt Ur Luv, Ur Lyf 2]] in 2007.<REF name=\"AutoJV-1\"/> He played Daniel the romantic interest of [[Isabelle Abiera]]'s character in Abt Ur Luv Ur Lyf 2<REF name=\"Young Stars\"/>\u2014his first TV role in 15 years after his television debut in [[Ang TV]].\n\nWhen Abt Ur Luv Ur Lyf 2 ended in 2008, he then went to appear in 2 other seasons of Star Magic Presents namely: [[Astigs|Astigs in Haay...skul Lyf]] and [[Astigs|Star Magic Presents: Astigs in Luvin' Lyf]].<ref name=\"Lauren\"/><ref name=\"Camsur\"/>\n\n==Personal life==\n\nAlfonso Martinez is the eldest and only son of actors [[Albert Martinez]] and Liezl Martinez.<REF name=\"Comeback\"/><REF name=\"Royalties\"/><ref name=\"Oki 1\"/> He has two younger sisters Alynna and Alyssa. He is a paternal nephew of [[William Martinez (actor)|William Martinez]] and [[Yayo Aguila]] and is also a maternal nephew of actors [[Aga Muhlach]] and [[Charlene Gonzales]]. His maternal grandparents are actors [[Amalia Fuentes]] and [[Romeo Vasquez]].<ref name=\"Apo\"/>\n\nMartinez has scoliosis.<ref name=\"Scoliosis\"/>\n\n== Filmography ==\n\n=== Television ===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" <!-- Do not center -->\n|- <!-- Never add unnecessary background colors -->\n! Year\n! Title\n! Role\n! class=\"unsortable\" | Notes <!-- Do not replace with or add a Network/Channel column. Network rivalry is outside of Wikipedia. Do not replace with an Episode column, Notes column is not limited to episode titles. -->\n! class=\"unsortable\" | Source <!-- Use third party sources other than the actor's IMDB page -->\n|- <!-- Do not add rowspan -->\n| 1992-94\n| ''[[Ang TV]]''\n| himself\n| Credited as \"''Alfons Martinez''\"\n| \n|-\n| 1993-94\n| ''[[Oki Doki Doc]]''\n| Fonzie\n| Credited as \"''Alfons Martinez''\"\n| <ref name